      <section eId="section_38">
        <heading>Value for Money (VfM)</heading>
        <intro>
          <p><b>Value for Money (VfM)</b></p>
        </intro>
        <paragraph>
          <num>50.</num>
          <content>
            <p>As this is a transfer, overall NPSV is neutral in all scenarios.  However, it is likely that with the added fee revenue, police can use existing resources elsewhere, reducing crime in other areas. Therefore, all options provide Value for Money. However, Option 3 is preferred option as it is the only option that provides significant cost-recovery which was the government’s manifesto commitment.</p>
          </content>
        </paragraph>
      </section>
